(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Figures of Speech.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind metaphor, simile,) Tj
T*
(personification, hyperbole, and effect.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct interpretation or writing method step by step instead of jumping to) Tj
T*
(the answer.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the result carefully and confirm that it matches the requirement of the topic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
